{"word":"προηγορέω","slug":"προηγορέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προηγορέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:προήγορος'><el>προήγορος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to speak on the part of</i> others, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>πρ. τινί</el> <i>to speak for</i> another, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}